      public override void DefaultVisit(SyntaxNode );

      public virtual void VisitLeadingTrivia(SyntaxToken );
      public virtual void VisitToken(SyntaxToken );
      public virtual void VisitTrailingTrivia(SyntaxToken );
      public virtual void VisitTrivia(SyntaxTrivia );

  public abstract class Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.CodeActions.CodeAction

    protected CodeAction();

    public virtual string EquivalenceKey { get; }
    public virtual ImmutableArray<string> Tags { get; }
    public abstract string Title { get; }

    protected virtual Task<IEnumerable<CodeActionOperation>> ComputeOperationsAsync(CancellationToken );
    protected virtual Task<IEnumerable<CodeActionOperation>> ComputePreviewOperationsAsync(CancellationToken );
    public static CodeAction Create(string , Func<CancellationToken, Task<Document>> , string  = null);
    public static CodeAction Create(string , Func<CancellationToken, Task<Solution>> , string  = null);
    protected virtual Task<Document> GetChangedDocumentAsync(CancellationToken );
    protected virtual Task<Solution> GetChangedSolutionAsync(CancellationToken );
    public Task<ImmutableArray<CodeActionOperation>> GetOperationsAsync(CancellationToken );
    public Task<ImmutableArray<CodeActionOperation>> GetPreviewOperationsAsync(CancellationToken );
